              <section class="section">
                <a id="main-content" tabindex="-1"></a>
                                    
<div id="block-un-base-theme-page-title" class="block block-core block-page-title-block block-un-base-theme-page-title">
  
    
      <div class="block-content block__content">
      
  <h1 class="title"><span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden">The right to a healthy environment: 6 things you need to know</span>
</h1>


    </div>
  </div>

<div class="views-element-container block block-views block-views-block-content-fields-block-lead" id="block-views-block-content-fields-block-lead">
  
    
      <div class="block-content block__content">
      <div><div class="view view-content-fields view-id-content_fields view-display-id-block_lead js-view-dom-id-a479d79812877d7dc79e9ccb177b517d7a6b0a499f009cc658eb78b02d8ea7dc">
  
    
      
      <div class="view-content">
          <div class="views-row">  <span class="views-field views-field-field-news-date"><span class="field-content"><time datetime="2021-10-15T12:00:00Z" class="datetime">15 October 2021</time>
</span></span><span class="views-field views-field-field-news-topics"><span class="field-content"><a href="/en/news/topic/climate-change" hreflang="en">Climate and Environment</a></span></span><div class="views-field views-field-field-news-story-lead"><div class="field-content"><p>On 8 October, loud and unusual applause reverberated around the chamber of the UN Human Rights Council in Geneva. A battle fought for decades by environmental activists and rights’ defenders, had finally borne fruit.</p>
</div></div></div>

    </div>
  
          </div>
</div>

    </div>
  </div>

